## Common Patterns Across Versions

### Error Handling Evolution
```
v1: if error_code != 0 { handle() }
v2: match result { Ok(x) => {}, Err(e) => {} }
v3: [same as v2, but AI suggests cases]
v4: match result.await { Ok(x) => {}, Err(e) => {} }
v5: [v4 with tracing]
v6: match result { Ok(x) => {}, Err(e) => recover() }
